      "Yes, variance can be computed in one pass:\r\n```python\r\nsum_vals = 0\r\nsum_squares = 0\r\ncount = 0\r\nfor value in stream:\r\n    sum_vals += value\r\n    sum_squares += value**2\r\n    count += 1\r\nvariance = sum_squares/count - (sum_vals/count)**2\r\n```\r\nEdit: corrected error in variance formula."
